summary:
Emphasizes the need for regular updates to MINUSTAH's planning documents, such as concepts of operations and rules of engagement, to align with relevant resolutions;

Requests the Secretary-General to report regularly on MINUSTAH's mandate implementation, semi-annually, and 45 days prior to its expiration;

Asks the Secretary-General to assess security threats in Haiti, propose options for MINUSTAH's consolidation and reconfiguration, and present a progress report on the consolidation plan;

Decides to remain seized of the matter.
